'''新加坡航空368号班机'''（SQ368）是一架由[[新加坡樟宜机场|新加坡樟宜机场]]飞往[[米兰-马尔彭萨机场|米兰-马尔彭萨机场]]的定期航班，2016年6月27日在前往米兰途中因引擎机油告灯亮起而折返樟宜机场，降落之后一个引擎随即着火。

==飛機==
這一事件涉及的飛機是[[波音777|波音777-312ER]]，事發時，飛機機齡九年。於2006年11月交付給新加坡航空公司，註冊編號為9V-SWB，生產序列號為33377，使用两台通用电气GE90-115B引擎。<ref>{{cite web |title=9V-SWB Aircraft Information |url=https://www.flightradar24.com/data/aircraft/9v-swb |website=FlightRadar24 |accessdate=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2016-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803122309/https://www.flightradar24.com/data/aircraft/9v-swb |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==事发经过==
2016年6月27日，飛行了兩個小時後，發動機燃油洩漏。飛機折返樟宜機場並安全降落。降落後右側發動機起火，導致右翼燒毀。機場消防部門撲滅了火。事件中沒有任何人員傷亡或受傷，但飛機機翼受到嚴重燒毀。<ref>{{cite|title=【新航驚魂】急降樟宜機場即起火 乘客：我剛死裏逃生|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20160627/55281982|accessdate=2016-06-28|archive-date=2017-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907164114/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20160627/55281982|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="channel-news-asia">{{cite news |title=SIA flight catches fire while making emergency landing in Singapore |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/sia-flight-catches-fire/2907544.html |accessdate=2016-06-27 |agency=Channel News Asia |archive-date=2016-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160627004859/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/sia-flight-catches-fire/2907544.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="daily-mail">{{cite news |last1=Devlin |first1=Peter |title=Terrified passengers film a Singapore Airlines plane bursting into flames on the runway after making an emergency landing |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3661493/Singapore-Airlines-flight-SQ368-plane-bound-Milan-catches-fire-Changi-Airport-emergency-landing.html |publisher=Daily Mail |date=2016-06-27 |accessdate=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2016-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160627062140/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3661493/Singapore-Airlines-flight-SQ368-plane-bound-Milan-catches-fire-Changi-Airport-emergency-landing.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="daily-mail" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://avherald.com/h?article=49a58209&opt=0 |title=Accident: Singapore B773 enroute on Jun 27th 2016, engine oil leak |publisher=The Aviation Herald |date=2016-06-27 |accessdate=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305085615/http://avherald.com/h?article=49a58209&opt=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Waldron, Greg |url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/fire-damage-apparent-on-s